75\u202f%**. The deal’s *expected margin* is 1.35\u202f% (above the minimum).  \n\n4. **Discount Limit** – The relationship discount applied is **0.45\u202f%**, equal to the maximum discount allowed by policy (0.45\u202f%). No excess discount.  \n\n5. **Policy Compliance Flag** – The structured data record already marks the deal as compliant (`policy_compliant = 1`).  \n\n**Verdict:** **Compliant** – All pricing elements (floor, margins, discount) meet FAB’s credit pricing policy for a low‑risk, internal rating\u202fA, AED term loan. No exception or additional approval is required.'}]}
