licy_floor** | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| **margin_below_min** | 0 | 1 | 0 |\n| **discount_exceeds_policy** | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| **policy_compliant** | 1 | 0 | 1 |\n\n*Source: `pricing_recommendation`*\n\n---\n\n### 📊 Profitability Summary\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **customer_id** | CUST001 |\n| **customer_segment** | SME |\n| **'}]}
