2026-06-25 06:10:21,936 | INFO     | agent_framework  | trace=c0c6c5477181f3282c4cb2fa52807fe0 span=120e5f9111f9dda7 parent=- | {'role': 'assistant', 'parts': [{'type': 'text', 'content': 'Based on the **FAB Credit Pricing Policy (v2.4)**, the minimum pricing floors for a **BB-rated** client depend on the product structure and facility tenor. All floors are expressed as spreads in basis points (bps) over the internal Funds Transfer Pricing (FTP) rate `[FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · 3]`.\n\n**1. Corporate Term Loans** `[FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · 3.1]`\n* **Tenor ≤ 1 Year:** 165 bps\n* **Tenor 1–3 Years:** 210 bps\n* **Tenor 3–5 Years:** 260 bps\n* **Tenor > 5 Years:** 320 bps\n\n**2. Revolving Credit Facilities (RCFs)** `[FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · 3.2]`\n* **Drawn Margin Floor:** 160 bps (plus tenor adjustments: +15 bps for tenor ≤3 years, +40 bps for tenor >3 years)\n* **Commitment Fee Floor:** 40 bps on undrawn portions\n* **Facility Fee Floor:** 20 bps\n\n**3. Relationship Value Adjustment** `[FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · 2.4]`\n* The required margin floor may be reduced by up to **25 bps** if the client demonstrates documented cross-sell revenues exceeding AED 500,000 per annum. This reduction requires prior approval from the relevant credit authority and annual review.\n\n*Note: Any pricing below these stated floors requires a formal Pricing Exception documented and approved per Section 6 of the policy.*'}]}
