2026-06-25 06:10:23,414 | INFO     | agent_framework  | trace=c0c6c5477181f3282c4cb2fa52807fe0 span=c4825282938e48d9 parent=- | {'role': 'assistant', 'parts': [{'type': 'text', 'content': '**Pricing Floors for a BB‑rated AED Loan (FAB Credit Pricing Policy\u202fv2.4)**  \n\n| Product | Tenor | Minimum Pricing Floor (bps over FTP) |\n|---------|-------|--------------------------------------|\n| **Corporate Term Loans** | ≤\u202f1\u202fYear | 165\u202fbps |\n| | 1\u202f–\u202f3\u202fYears | 210\u202fbps |\n| | 3\u202f–\u202f5\u202fYears | 260\u202fbps |\n| | >\u202f5\u202fYears | 320\u202fbps |\n| **Revolving Credit Facilities (RCFs)** | Drawn Margin (base) | 160\u202fbps |\n| | + Tenor\u202fadjustment (≤\u202f3\u202fyr) | +15\u202fbps |\n| | + Tenor\u202fadjustment (>\u202f3\u202fyr) | +40\u202fbps |\n| | Commitment Fee (undrawn) | 40\u202fbps |\n| | Facility Fee | 20\u202fbps |\n\n**Relationship Value Adjustment** – The margin floor may be reduced by up to **25\u202fbps** if the client generates documented cross‑sell revenues\u202f>\u202fAED\u202f500,000\u202fpa, subject to credit‑authority approval (Section\u202f2.4).\n\n> *“Any pricing below these stated floors requires a formal Pricing Exception documented and approved per Section\u202f6 of the policy.”*  \n\n**Source:** query_knowledge_base → *FAB Credit Pricing Policy (v2.4)*, Sections\u202f3.1,\u202f3.2,\u202f2.4,\u202f6.'}]}
