r | 0 (No) | 0 (No) | 0 (No) |\n| • Margin below minimum | 0 (No) | **1 (Yes)** | 0 (No) |\n| • Discount exceeds policy | 0 (No) | 0 (No) | 0 (No) |\n| **Policy Compliant** | **1 (Yes)** | **0 (No)** | **1 (Yes)** |\n\n**Key Takeaways:**\n* **DEAL033 & DEAL041** were approved at `6.80%` and `6.50%` respectively, both remaining fully compliant with pricing and margin policies.\n* **DEAL040** was priced at `5.45%`, but flagged as **non-compliant** because the expected margin (`-0.50%`) fell below the policy minimum expected margin (`0.10%`). This contributed to the deal outcome being marked as `Lost`.\n\n*(Source: pricing_recommendation)*'}]}
