2026-06-25 14:44:17,945 | INFO     | agent_framework  | trace=17526f8301c2587d1a9c4a1b3212db85 span=3b1464b465b33838 parent=- | {'role': 'assistant', 'parts': [{'type': 'text', 'content': 'Based on **FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4**, the minimum pricing floors for **BB-rated AED Corporate Term Loans** are applied as a spread over the applicable Funds Transfer Pricing (FTP) rate. The floors vary by facility tenor as follows:\n\n| Facility Tenor | Minimum Pricing Floor (Spread over FTP) |\n|----------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| **≤ 1 Year**       | 165 bps                                   |\n| **1–3 Years**      | 210 bps                                   |\n| **3–5 Years**      | 260 bps                                   |\n| **> 5 Years**      | 320 bps                                   |\n\n**Important Policy Notes:**\n* **All-in Rate Calculation:** The floors represent the absolute minimum spread. The total all-in rate must not fall below `Applicable FTP Rate + Stated Floor Spread` ([FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · Section 3]).\n* **Revolving Credit Facilities (RCFs):** If the facility is structured as an RCF, the drawn margin floor for a BB-rated client (tenure ≤ 3 years) is **160 bps** over FTP, plus a commitment fee floor of 40 bps and facility fee floor of 20 bps ([FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · Section 3.2]).\n* **Pricing Exceptions:** Pricing below these floors is prohibited without a formally documented and approved Pricing Exception ([FAB_Credit_Pricing_Policy_v2.4 · Section 6]).'}]}
